	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Remark</span>
	It follows from condition (iii) above that if $K$ is a compact subset of $\mathcal{G}$, then $\sup_{x\in\mathcal{G}^{(0)}}\lambda^x(K)\smallerthan\infty$.
